clean: false
[ORG024] Warning: remote table reference is missing a closing `)`
@ fixture.org:5:1
fix: write TBLFM assignments as supported Org table targets with non-empty right-hand sides
line: 5 | #+TBLFM: $2=$1::$2=$99::bad-lhs=$1::@99=$1::$1=remote(other,$1
Help: remote table reference is missing a closing `)`
Contract: TBLFM formulas should use Org-supported left-hand targets and complete assignments before table tooling consumes them.

[ORG024] Warning: table formula left-hand side `bad-lhs` is not an Org table target
@ fixture.org:5:1
fix: write TBLFM assignments as supported Org table targets with non-empty right-hand sides
line: 5 | #+TBLFM: $2=$1::$2=$99::bad-lhs=$1::@99=$1::$1=remote(other,$1
Help: table formula left-hand side `bad-lhs` is not an Org table target
Contract: TBLFM formulas should use Org-supported left-hand targets and complete assignments before table tooling consumes them.

[ORG025] Warning: table formula target `$2` is defined 2 times in one TBLFM line
@ fixture.org:5:1
fix: keep one formula assignment per TBLFM target in each active TBLFM line
line: 5 | #+TBLFM: $2=$1::$2=$99::bad-lhs=$1::@99=$1::$1=remote(other,$1
Help: table formula target `$2` is defined 2 times in one TBLFM line
Contract: Each TBLFM target should have one active definition so agents and exporters do not guess which formula wins.

[ORG026] Warning: table formula column reference `$99` points outside 2 table columns
@ fixture.org:5:1
fix: point table formula row and column references inside the current table shape
line: 5 | #+TBLFM: $2=$1::$2=$99::bad-lhs=$1::@99=$1::$1=remote(other,$1
Help: table formula column reference `$99` points outside 2 table columns
Contract: Absolute table formula references should stay within the table rows and columns visible to this parser projection.

